name: Smile challenge
content: During one hour smile at everyone you pass by, you don t have to be insistent.  Once, three persons smile you back you win the xp !

name: Small talk
content: Speak with people you see often to, e.g receptionist at work, it could be anyone. Once,  you spoke with someone for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: The voice
content: Sing loudly in your room, in the shower and in the kitchen, Make your voice heard.  Once, you are tired  you win the xp !

name: Talk in the shop
content: Engage in conversations with people in shops “how is your day?”  Once,  you spoke with someone for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: Call the manager
content: Call up a company up to inquire about something (at home).  Once,  you spoke with someone for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: Call a person
content: Call someone you know that you haven’t spoken to for a chat. Once,  you spoke with someone for more than ten minutes, you win the xp !

name: Direction
content: Ask a stranger on the street for directions/time. Once,  you get your destination/time, you win the xp !

name: posture
content: Look at your posture in mirror and practice talking with your hands. Once, you like your posture and gesture, you win the xp !

name: Shop conversation
content: Ask someone in a shop for help and then engage them in conversation. Once,  you spoke with someone for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: new gym class
content: Do a new class at the gym and talk to the instructor about it. Once,  you spoke with the instructor for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: restaurent recommendation
content: Engage a stranger in further conversation, for example asking for recommendation for a good restaurant. Once,  you spoke with someone for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: flash outfit
content: Wear a bold outfit/bright lip colour and make people look at you

name: Suggest idea
content: Suggest a new idea to your boss. Speak confidently and slowly. Once,  you spoketo your boss for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: Lunch with colleague
content: Ask colleague to go for lunch with you and don’t take your phone so you have to engage in conversation. Once,  your colleague accept, you win the xp !

name: meetup
content: Go to a ‘meet up’ group on your own and talk to people. Once,  you spoke with someone for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: Gym conversation
content: Speak to three people at gym. Once,  you speak with three people, you win the xp !

name: Leader
content: Arrange a meeting at work and lead it. Once, you lead the meeting,  you win the xp !

name: Have a lunch
content: Ask an acquaintance out for lunch and engage in conversation. Once an acquaintance accept th lunch, you win the xp !

name: Phone complaint
content: Ring a company and make a complaint. Once,  you spoke with someone for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: Stop Sorry
content: Don’t use the word sorry ALL DAY. Once, you don t use a sorry all day long, you win the xp !

name: Eat alone
content: Eat in a restaurant on your own. Once, you pay your bill, you win the xp !

name: Speak with people
content: Speak to 3 new people today. Once,  you speak with three people, you win the xp !

name: Be funny
content: Tell a joke in front of a big group of people. Once, you finish your joke in front of the group, you win the xp !

name: Know your colleague
content: Spend lunch getting to know a colleague. Once,  you spoketo a colleague  for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: Speaking course
content: Book a public speaking course. Once you reach the speaking course, you win the xp !

name: Coffe shop
content: Go to a coffee shop and read a book for a few hours. Speak to 3 people. Once,  you speak with three people, you win the xp !

name: Social event
content: Go to a social event on your own and talk to 3 new people. Once,  you speak with three people, you win the xp !

name: Dancing time !
place: In a bar or a club
content: Go for a night out SOBER and dance and talk to people. Once,  you spoke with someone for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: Giving is caring
content: Give $5 to Five Random People. Once, you give the $25 to five random people, you win the xp !

name: Greeting game
content: Greet people at cofee . Once, you great more than 5 people, you win the xp !

name: Dating time
content: Ask a girl/guy out to Dinner. Once, you get you meeting, you win the xp !

name: Rate my look (please)
content: Ask Strangers to Rate My Look. Once, 3 people rate your look, you win the xp !

name: Hello stranger
content: Say hello to people you come across. Once you say hello to 5 people, you win the xp !

name: Be nice
content: Genuinely compliment someone. Once you compliment 5 people, you win the xp !

name: Dare to critisize
content: Say a constructive critisism to someone. Once you say a construtive critisism to 2 poeple,  you win the xp !

name: Meet with people
content: Ask someone you like for a date. Once, you get you meeting, you win the xp !

name: Say NO!
content: Say no to a proposition you don't like. Once, you say no to a proposition you don't like,  you win the xp !

name: The speeker
content: Speak in front of a large audience.  Once,  you spoke with someone for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: Listen to people
content: Have a conversation solely about the other person's interests.  Once,  you spoke with someone for more than ten  minutes, you win the xp !

name: Take a pic'
content: Pictures with Strangers. Once, you have a pictures with 3 people, you win the xp !

name: Charity
content: Get Donation For Charity on The Street. Once, 2 people accept, you win the xp !

name: Express yourself
content: Express a need. Once, you express your need to  3 people, you win the xp !

name: Make a plan
content: Plan an outside activity with your relatives. Once the relative and you are doing the activity, you win the xp !

name: The chatter
content: Start a conversation with your relatives. Once,  you spoke with someone for more than ten minutes, you win the xp !

name: Dare to watch
content: Ask 2 of your relative to go to the cinema with you. Once, your 2 relatives accept, you win the xp !

name: Walk together
content: Ask 2 of your relative to go for a walk in a park. Once, your 2 relatives accept, you win the xp !

name: Let's have a drink
content: Ask 2 of your relative to go have a drink in a bar. your 2 relatives accept, you win the xp !

name: Meet other darer
content: Meet a stranger and talk with him. Once,  you spoke with a stranger for more than five minutes, you win the xp !

name: Come to me
content: Meet a stranger at your place. Once, the stranger is at your place, you win the xp !

name: Let's do something
content: Ask a stranger to do an activity with you. Once, you are doing the activity with the stranger, you win the xp !

name: Have a drink
content: Meet a stranger at the bar. Once, you meet the stranger at the bar, you win the xp !

name: Share your feeling
content: Talk to a stranger about one your problem. Once,  you spoke with someone for more than ten minutes, you win the xp !

name: High five !
content: Meet a stranger and high-five him. Once, you high five 3 strangers,  you win the xp

name: Practice together
content: Ask a stranger to have a sport session with you. Once, you have a sport session with a stranger, you win the xp !
